flowRoot.flowPara: This SVG drawing is based on the original PNG logo of the project Augeas. There were no vector version of the logo for icons and other usages. So, I reversed engineered the drawing to vectorize it.
The drawing has been done with the help of an axonometric grid of 30 degrees.
Original logo's font is (most likely) Proxima Nova A, but it's a non-free font, so it was replaced here by Inder (SIL OFL).
